{"tid":2255320,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人諗過熊先係幕後邪惡大佬?","createTime":"2020-10-23T12:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T13:04:26.000Z","uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2da91fc355a3e9211340dc798d53537c54c858be","tid":2255320,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:33:15.000Z","msg":"irene閪就一定<br />\n但係有冇人諗過點解啤啤每場風暴每張gif圖, 最後結果都係一啲成員受損而熊受益?<br />\n攞毛巾畀耶妹疑似畀佢推開, 一單唔使一日就畀人debunk到嘅霸凌傳聞<br />\n加埋呢單, 叻啤入面最受同情嘅又係同irene相處最多最耐嘅熊<br />\n有冇咁啱得咁橋? 有冇諗過全部都係熊精心經營出嚟?<br />\n你可能會問, 一個人有冇可能假到咁盡又咁聰明?<br />\n我同你講, 有, 嗰個人叫史太林<br />\n二十年代蘇聯權鬥, 史太林就係靠住扮中庸無害, 引到各個派別推佢打另一派<br />\n到各派逐一被打殘時先發現, 已經冇任何人阻止到佢成為獨裁者<br />\n殷鑑不遠, 我身為一個資深啤啤飯真係想提醒各位<br />\n要捧呢個熊, be careful what  you wish for"},{"pid":"5fa29dfc5a8664796646f6dea46d121ec4ed377d","tid":2255320,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"要捧呢個熊, be careful what you wish for<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475e17b8d63176cf4ca168c9c7951bccfb36a732","tid":2255320,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fa29dfc5a8664796646f6dea46d121ec4ed377d","tid":2255320,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"要捧呢個熊, be careful what you wish for<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src